FREE STATE - Francé Grobler was shocked when her boyfriend, Wouter van der Merwe, appeared to become involved in an altercation with officials who had pulled him over. To her delight, the reality was something very different. Francé is seen accepting Wouter's marriage proposal in the video posted on Facebook. The couple subsequently enjoyed a romantic weekend at the Verkykerskop Estate in Free State. Wouter extended his thanks to the police officers who helped him make his marriage proposal special. eNCA